snippet.title: EXODUS Official Cinematic Reveal Trailer | The Game Awards 2023
snippet.description:
EXODUS was announced at The Game Awards 2023 and is an epic new sci-fi action-adventure role-playing game franchise developed by the team at Archetype Entertainment. Produced by Blur Studio. BECOME THE TRAVELER.

#tga2023 #exodus #gaming
